{"tid":2188076,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"預知，未來，超遠端技術？","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T14:53:59.000Z","uid":70883,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5d90e12ca3c4becac386af6770c5e5dbc969fcad","tid":2188076,"uid":70883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"一般人的智能手機、電腦等，不再需要強大的核心/圖像處理器，所有運算工作都由中央電腦處理。<br />\n<br />\n中央電腦即是由商業公司所架設的超級電腦，並以虛擬軟件來架構、摸擬個人化的電腦環境及儲存空間。<br />\n<br />\n一般人只需透過所具備簡單硬件的個人電腦，以網絡來遠端控制中央電腦，一般人從螢幕所見的，只是經網絡傳播的即時畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發展條件<br />\n1.極高速的網絡<br />\n2.極穩定的網絡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.價錢<br />\n2.輕巧<br />\n3.高畫質遊戲門檻<br />\n4.繪圖多工處理<br />\n5.用電量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題：<br />\n1.價錢<br />\n2.商業利潤<br />\n3.個人私隱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實則只是有感而發，並非善於該領域，歡迎各位討論長短。"},{"pid":"07471830e1fb1c77cb9d0b67f53f0c5387f3b581","tid":2188076,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"Old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c62e3e34c2d923db12b84c93ea5a9dc941e522","tid":2188076,"uid":87820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"咪有囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1879f205e1b506abd9bd41b85a3b21f2a00e4ec2","tid":2188076,"uid":70883,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"有啊沒錯，但現時好像沒商業公司為普通人架構這個?<br />\n而且想討論未來會否成為一種普及性。"},{"pid":"1542d0b49361d7901fdfb06ae87fe956b4d26eb6","tid":2188076,"uid":116289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"GeForce NOW"},{"pid":"d46b025c80994dfb07263ffe39684f53e1d4f427","tid":2188076,"uid":70883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1542d0b49361d7901fdfb06ae87fe956b4d26eb6","tid":2188076,"uid":116289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1